{
  "stem": "14002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the whole deal of a bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't like here, in the United States, where you spend all your fortunes on the bar mitzvah, where a child doesn't even know well to say the 'Baruch' and-- and after.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then after that-- that was in August.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that, my mother send me about 80-- 80 kilometers from our town, in a yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The name of that town was Beregsaz, in Czechoslovakian, Berehovo",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there a year, in that yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that, it started in 1938, '39, when Hitler marched into Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- and then our-- our-- our town-- not our town, but the whole-- whole part of that became Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Hungarian took it over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in 1941-- in 1941, they made a law that-- no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1940, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1940, they made a law that every Jew has to prove his birthplace, where he was born.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But unfortunately, those what couldn't-- what didn't-- what made a joke out of it, in 1941, one Saturday-- one Saturday, the only way you-- you could-- the only way you could-- you could bring the-- the town together, when you want to announce something, is there was a guy with a drum.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like years ago, they used to say, hear ye, hear ye!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The same way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went with a drum.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he called out that all the Jews, what cannot prove-- what cannot prove that they are born here as citizens, have to assemble tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Unfortunately, my grandfather, but his grandfather was born in that town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had to go with-- with our grandmother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My uncle, what he used to live next to us, he had eight children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a butcher, by the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
